  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0da7\u0db1\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dallas President comes to the fray",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Minister Dallas Alahapperuma said that he is also contesting for the presidency.",
        "Meanwhile, political sources say that several other names are under discussion for the presidency"
      ],
